
# a func to execute lambda
xizmatchi f o'zgaruvch x ff mazmuni
    Iltimos ff bilan x 3 ishlatilsin va r olinsin
    buyruq r yozilsin
tamomlansin

# func call that declare a lambda (args coount is $0, arg1 is $1, ...)
Iltimos f bilan 10 {
    o'zgaruvch t qiymati 0 bo'lsin
    t = $1 * $2
    natija t qaytarilsin
} ishlatilsin va r olinsin